results.title: Llama lovers perfect tee. Live, laugh, love in Llama language - Funny  llama Tee. Llamazing.
results.description:
Funny Llama lovers Tee. 

Printing Method:
Sublimation. It is ink that is dyed into the fibers of the shirt, it does not just sit on top of the shirt. This means you do not have that slick feeling of vinyl, it will never be cracked, faded, or come off.

Sizes Available:
Adult Unisex XS-2XL

Style:
High quality, unisex fit tee that is true to size.

Fabric: 
Heather Grey and White are 100 % Polyester.
All other colors are Poly- Cotton Blend (60/40).

Care instructions: 
Machine wash cold. Tumble dry low. Do not use bleach or fabric softener.

Shipping and Delivery:
All apparel is hand-printed in order. We'll need 1-3 business days to print and package your order. We ship USPS First Class mail. Shipping time is also 3-4 days. Please consider this when ordering for a special event. During busy time please allow 1-5 days for processing. We will not issue a refund or accept a return if your order does not arrive at you on the expected delivery date. Please understand that all of our shirts are made to order and when we ship them out, we no longer have control over when it's delivered. We operate in good faith and try to get everyone's orders out in time and get them to you when you need them.
We'll send confirmation and tracking when your order has shipped.

Contact us:
Absolutely!!! Please use the envelope icon to send us a message and we will answer you as soon as we can!

Exchange/Return Policy:
All Sales are final due to the custom nature of the order. Please Please Please Pay Attention when placing your order. All shirt sizes are UNISEX and are true to size. Size Recommendation is listed above. We do not process exchanges. We are not responsible if your order is shipped to the wrong address due to your mistake and will not give refunds or send a second item. If the tracking information on your order shows that it has been delivered to the address on your order, we cannot be held responsible for any lost or misplaced packages and will not send another item. If the USPS returns your package to us, you must pay shipping for us to resend it.

Order Cancellations:
We do NOT accept order cancellations if we have already begun working on your order. Each shirt is made to order especially for you. If we do approve your cancellation, it will be subject to a 15% cancellation fee.

Feedback:
We appreciate your feedback! If you have a problem or concern, please let us know! We try our best to put out the best quality products and we love it when our customers love their purchase! :)

Note: 
Shirts may be cuffed and knotted in the listing picture. They will not arrive at you that way, but if you like the look you can roll up the sleeves and tie the knot to fit your style when you wear it.

Photos displayed in this listing are digitally generated to best show the shirt design. Actual graphic sizing and color may differ on the final product depending on the size of the shirt and your screen resolution.

results.title: Book folding pattern for LIVE LOVE LAUGH set of 3 patterns
results.description:
© Angela Jarmin - 'Patterns for Pages' ALL RIGHTS RESERVED. This pattern contains material protected under UK and International Copyright Laws and Treaties. Any unauthorized reprint or use of this material is prohibited. No part of this pattern file may be reproduced or transmitted in any form or by any means, electronic or mechanical, including photocopying, recording, or by any information storage and retrieval system without express written permission from the author / publisher.
I do authorise the sale of completed books made from my patterns.


Turn your pre-loved books into re-loved art & gifts.

This listing is for a book folding pattern to fold LIVE, LOVE & LAUGH into 3 separate hardback books to create an artistic addition as a gift or for your home or office.  You can even sell the finished folded book. 

LIVE requires 516 pages, that's 258 folds
LOVE requires 530 pages, that's 265 folds  (THIS PATTERN IS ALSO AVAILABLE SEPERATELY)
LAUGH requires 574 pages, that's 287 folds
Each pattern has been created for a book height of 20 cms (excluding the covers) but it can be folded into a taller book, it’ll just leave you a little extra space below the image, for wider ribbon maybe.

All of my patterns are measure & mark, the most popular method to create folded book art.  All of my patterns are tried & tested, you won’t encounter a ‘bad pattern’ here, the photo shows you exactly what your book will look like, providing you follow the pattern correctly of course.

Your pattern is downloadable as a pdf file as soon as your payment is confirmed.  You’ll need a program that can open & print pdf files of course (Adobe Reader is free of charge & perfect for this).

Book folding is a fascinating hobby, so easy to mark out and fold as and when you have some spare time.  It doesn’t need to be done all in one ‘sitting’.  Mark a few pages on the train, fold a few pages in your lunch break, it’s easy to do but looks so unique.  All you need is a hardback book, a ruler & a pencil, that’s it.  Some people decorate the covers of their books, others fold an image relating to the title of the book, the possibilities are endless.

To find instructions on how to fold, there is a very good guide on Instructables here http://www.instructables.com/id/Folded-Book-Art-Best-most-clear-Tutorial-available/step2/Marking-the-pages/

Be sure to add Patterns for Pages to your favorites and come back often to see new patterns.

I also undertake commissioned patterns on an untested basis at the reduce cost of £2.50 per pattern.  Get your thinking cap on & request something unique by emailing me at patternsforpages@gmail.com or ask a question using the button above to the right.

We decided to put it on a sign then we also decided we needed to make it for daughters too. Any of your grown children would appreciate this sign.  This handpainted laser engraved sign is made to order. 

We can also change any wording or leave just the way we have created. Personalized gifts make a great way to go, everyone loves the special touch!

* This sign measures approximately 12 x 16 inches and is on 3/8 inch blondewood.

* Creation is shown in BarnRed/AntiqueWhite.  Several other color options available in drop down selection. The first color will be the color of the text & second color will be the background.

* If we are shipping directly as gift, we can enclose a small handwritten note card, be sure to let us know what you want the card to say in the NOTES section when you order.

* For PERSONALIZED signs or signs you want modified please put the information in the NOTES section when placing order.

We have over 700 items in this Etsy shop so be sure to take a look around in the different sections we offer. https://www.etsy.com/shop/ExpressionsNmore?ref=hdr_shop_menu

Also Be sure to check out our 2nd Etsy shop which includes color creations from the use of our LED UV flatbed https://www.etsy.com/shop/ExpressionsNmoreVer2?ref=listing-shop2-all-items-count#items

* PROCESS Our handcrafted creations are made using a 7 step process to create a beautiful expression to be cherished for years to come. Two contrasting colors of paint are applied, the design is laser engraved, a fine hairline is applied to the design which gives an awesome touch. The final touches are completed once it goes through our antiquing process with edges distressed.

Keep in mind when selecting the color options, the first color is the text color, while the second color is the background. See policies for additional questions/clarification on colors.

*When working with wood and the antiquing process, each sign has its own warmth and charm. While we try to get the best wood at the lumber yard, sometimes there will be knots or other slight imperfections in the wood, this is considered adding character to the rustic style of this line of our signs.
